{"format": "tiptap/v1", "updatedAt": "2026-06-21T15:09:22.709Z", "doc": {"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Time/Space Tradeoffs"}, {"type": "text", "text": " are algorithm design strategies where you sacrifice memory (space) to gain speed (time) or vice versa. The core principle: "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "use more storage to precompute/cache results for O(1) lookup vs. recompute for O(n) time"}, {"type": "text", "text": ", or "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "use minimal storage and recompute for O(1) space vs. O(n) time"}, {"type": "text", "text": ". In Gen AI, these tradeoffs are critical for "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "transformer optimization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (caching attention weights), "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "model quantization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (smaller models vs. recomputation), "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LLM response caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (O(1) cache vs. O(n) generation), and "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "prefix caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (pre-computed tokens for faster inference)."}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"src": "data:image/svg+xml;base64,", "alt": "Time/Space Tradeoffs — concept overview"}}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What It Is"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Aspect"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Definition"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Purpose"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Core Idea"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Trade memory for speed or speed for memory"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Optimize algorithm based on constraints"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Time-Space Trade-off"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "More space → less time (precompute/cache)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fast lookup, avoid redundant computation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Space-Time Trade-off"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Less space → more time (recompute)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Memory-efficient, slower execution"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data Storage"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Uncompressed = more space, less time"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Compressed = less space, more time"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Lookup Tables"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Precompute → O(1) vs. recalc → O(n)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Cache results for repeated queries"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Why It Matters for Gen AI"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ❌ WITHOUT tradeoff: Recompute every time (slow, O(n))\n# LLM generation: Generate response from scratch each query\ndef generate_response_slow(query):\n    # ❌ O(n) generation: 2-5 seconds per query\n    response = llm.generate(query)  # ❌ Slow: full computation\n    return response\n\ngenerate_response_slow(\"Explain quantum computing\")  # ❌ 2-5 seconds\ngenerate_response_slow(\"Explain quantum computing\")  # ❌ 2-5 seconds (recompute!)\n\n# ✅ WITH tradeoff: Cache for O(1) lookup (fast, O(1))\n# LLM caching: Store responses for repeated queries\ncache = {}  # ✅ Hash table for O(1) lookup\n\ndef generate_response_fast(query):\n    if query in cache:  # ✅ O(1) cache check\n        return cache[query]  # ✅ Instant: O(1) [web:258][web:261]\n    \n    # ❌ O(n) generation only for new queries\n    response = llm.generate(query)  # ❌ 2-5 seconds\n    cache[query] = response  # ✅ Store for future [web:258][web:261]\n    return response\n\ngenerate_response_fast(\"Explain quantum computing\")  # ❌ 2-5 seconds (first time)\ngenerate_response_fast(\"Explain quantum computing\")  # ✅ Instant (cached!) [web:258][web:261]"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Key benefits:"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Speed vs memory"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Trade O(n) → O(1) with cache\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformer optimization"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Cache attention weights for faster inference\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Model quantization"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Smaller models (less space) vs. recomputation (more time)\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LLM caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": O(1) cache vs. O(n) generation for repeated queries\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Prefix caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Pre-computed tokens for faster inference"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Common Time/Space Tradeoff Techniques ⭐"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memoization (Caching Results)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Memoization: O(1) cache vs O(n) recomputation\ndef fibonacci_memo(n, memo={}):\n    if n in memo:  # ✅ O(1) cache check\n        return memo[n]  # ✅ Instant: O(1) [web:258][web:261]\n    \n    if n <= 1:  # ✅ Base case\n        return n\n    \n    # ❌ O(n) computation only if not cached\n    memo[n] = fibonacci_memo(n - 1, memo) + fibonacci_memo(n - 2, memo)  # ✅ Store\n    return memo[n]  # ✅ O(n) with memoization [web:258][web:261]\n\nfibonacci_memo(50)  # ❌ First call: O(n)\nfibonacci_memo(50)  # ✅ Second call: O(1) (cached!) [web:258][web:261]\n# Time: O(n) → O(1) with memoization, Space: O(n) for cache [web:258][web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Lookup Tables (Precomputation)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Lookup Table: O(1) precompute vs O(n) recalc\ndef precompute_squares(max_n):\n    lookup = {}  # ✅ Hash table for O(1) lookup\n    for i in range(max_n + 1):\n        lookup[i] = i * i  # ✅ Precompute: O(n)\n    return lookup\n\nlookup = precompute_squares(1000000)  # ✅ Precompute once: O(n)\n\ndef get_square(n):\n    return lookup[n]  # ✅ O(1) lookup (vs O(1) compute, but reused) [web:258][web:264]\n\nget_square(999999)  # ✅ Instant: O(1) (vs O(1) compute, but reused) [web:258][web:264]\n# Time: O(1) lookup vs O(1) compute (repeated use), Space: O(n) for table [web:258][web:264]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Prefix Caching (LLM Inference)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Prefix Caching: Cache pre-computed tokens for faster inference\nprefix_cache = {}  # ✅ Cache for O(1) prefix lookup\n\ndef llm_inference_with_prefix(prompt, max_tokens=100):\n    # ✅ Step 1: Check if prefix cached\n    prefix = prompt[:50]  # ✅ First 50 tokens as prefix\n    if prefix in prefix_cache:  # ✅ O(1) cache check\n        cached_tokens = prefix_cache[prefix]  # ✅ Instant: O(1)\n        # ✅ Use cached + generate remaining\n        return cached_tokens + generate_remaining(prompt, max_tokens - len(cached_tokens))\n    \n    # ❌ Step 2: Generate full response (slow)\n    response = generate_full(prompt, max_tokens)  # ❌ 2-5 seconds\n    prefix_cache[prefix] = response  # ✅ Cache for future\n    return response\n\nllm_inference_with_prefix(\"Quantum computing is...\")  # ❌ First: 2-5s\nllm_inference_with_prefix(\"Quantum computing is...\")  # ✅ Cached: Instant [web:261]\n# Time: O(1) cached vs O(n) generate, Space: O(total_tokens) for cache [web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "4. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Dynamic Programming (Tabulation)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ DP Tabulation: O(n) space → O(n) time (vs O(n) space → O(2ⁿ) time)\ndef knapsack_dp(items, capacity):\n    n = len(items)\n    dp = [[0] * (capacity + 1) for _ in range(n + 1)]  # ✅ O(n × capacity) space [web:258][web:261]\n    \n    for i in range(1, n + 1):\n        weight, value = items[i - 1]\n        for w in range(capacity + 1):\n            dp[i][w] = dp[i - 1][w]  # ✅ Don't include\n            if w >= weight:\n                dp[i][w] = max(dp[i][w], dp[i - 1][w - weight] + value)  # ✅ Include [web:258][web:261]\n    \n    return dp[n][capacity]  # ✅ O(n × capacity) time [web:258][web:261]\n\nitems = [(10, 60), (20, 100), (30, 120)]  # (weight, value)\nknapsack_dp(items, 50)  # ✅ 220 (optimal)\n# Time: O(n × capacity), Space: O(n × capacity) (vs O(2ⁿ) brute force) [web:258][web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "5. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Compression (Space ↓, Time ↑)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Compression: Less space, more time (decompression)\nimport gzip\n\n# ❌ Uncompressed: More space, less time (instant read)\ndata_uncompressed = \"Large dataset about AI...\"  # ✅ 10MB\ndata_uncompressed  # ✅ Instant: O(1) read [web:258]\n\n# ✅ Compressed: Less space, more time (decompress)\ndata_compressed = gzip.compress(data_uncompressed)  # ✅ 1MB (10x smaller)\ndata_decompressed = gzip.decompress(data_compressed)  # ❌ 0.1s (decompress) [web:258]\n\n# Time: O(1) uncompressed vs O(decompress_time) compressed, Space: 10MB vs 1MB [web:258]"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Tradeoff Techniques ⭐"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Technique"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Time ↓ (Faster)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Space ↑ (More Memory)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Case"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memoization"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(1) cached vs O(n) recompute"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(n) cache"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Fibonacci, DP, recursion"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Lookup Tables"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(1) precompute vs O(n) recalc"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(n) table"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Math functions, precomputed values"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Prefix Caching"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(1) cached vs O(n) generate"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(total_tokens) cache"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "LLM inference, repeated queries"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Dynamic Programming"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(n) vs O(2ⁿ) brute force"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(n × capacity) table"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Knapsack, LCS, edit distance"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Compression"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(decompress_time)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1/10th size (10MB → 1MB)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "File storage, database"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Data Indexing"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(log n) index vs O(n) scan"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "O(n) index"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Database queries, search"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Gen AI Applications ⭐"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "1. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Transformer Attention Caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Transformer: Cache attention weights for O(1) reuse (vs O(n²) compute)\nattention_cache = {}  # ✅ Cache for O(1) lookup\n\ndef transformer_attention_with_cache(tokens, layer_idx):\n    token_key = tuple(tokens)  # ✅ Hashable key\n    \n    if token_key in attention_cache and layer_idx in attention_cache[token_key]:  # ✅ O(1) check\n        return attention_cache[token_key][layer_idx]  # ✅ Instant: O(1) [web:261]\n    \n    # ❌ O(n²) compute attention (slow)\n    attention = compute_attention(tokens, layer_idx)  # ❌ 2-5s for 1000 tokens [web:261]\n    \n    # ✅ Cache for future\n    if token_key not in attention_cache:\n        attention_cache[token_key] = {}\n    attention_cache[token_key][layer_idx] = attention\n    \n    return attention\n\ntransformer_attention_with_cache(token_ids, layer_idx=0)  # ❌ First: O(n²)\ntransformer_attention_with_cache(token_ids, layer_idx=0)  # ✅ Cached: O(1) [web:261]\n# Time: O(1) cached vs O(n²) compute, Space: O(total_tokens × layers) [web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "2. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Model Quantization (Space ↓, Time ↑)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Quantization: Smaller model (less space) vs. dequantization (more time)\n# FP32: 4 bytes per parameter → INT8: 1 byte per parameter (4x smaller) [web:261]\n\n# ❌ Unquantized: More space, less time (fast inference)\nmodel_fp32 = load_model(\"large_llm\", dtype=\"fp32\")  # ✅ 10GB (4 bytes per param)\noutput_fp32 = model_fp32.generate(prompt)  # ✅ Fast: O(1) dequant [web:261]\n\n# ✅ Quantized: Less space, more time (dequantization overhead)\nmodel_int8 = load_model(\"large_llm\", dtype=\"int8\")  # ✅ 2.5GB (1 byte per param) [web:261]\noutput_int8 = model_int8.generate(prompt)  # ❌ Slower: O(dequant_time) [web:261]\n\n# Time: O(1) FP32 vs O(dequant) INT8, Space: 10GB vs 2.5GB (4x smaller) [web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "3. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LLM Response Caching (O(1) vs O(n))"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ LLM Caching: O(1) cache vs O(n) generation (repeated queries)\nresponse_cache = {}  # ✅ Hash table for O(1) lookup\n\ndef llm_generation_with_cache(prompt):\n    if prompt in response_cache:  # ✅ O(1) cache check\n        return response_cache[prompt]  # ✅ Instant: O(1) [web:258][web:261]\n    \n    # ❌ O(n) generation (slow)\n    response = llm.generate(prompt)  # ❌ 2-5 seconds\n    response_cache[prompt] = response  # ✅ Cache for future [web:258][web:261]\n    return response\n\nllm_generation_with_cache(\"What is AI?\")  # ❌ First: 2-5s\nllm_generation_with_cache(\"What is AI?\")  # ✅ Cached: Instant [web:258][web:261]\n# Time: O(1) cached vs O(n) generate, Space: O(total_responses) [web:258][web:261]"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 4}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "4. "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Prefix-Tuning (Pre-computation)"}, {"type": "text", "text": " ⭐"}]}, {"type": "codeBlock", "attrs": {"language": "python"}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "# ✅ Prefix-Tuning: Pre-compute prefix embeddings for faster inference\nprefix_embeddings = {}  # ✅ Cache for O(1) prefix lookup\n\ndef llm_prefix_tuning(prompt, prefix_id=\"common_prefix\"):\n    if prefix_id in prefix_embeddings:  # ✅ O(1) cache check\n        prefix_emb = prefix_embeddings[prefix_id]  # ✅ Instant: O(1)\n    else:\n        prefix_emb = compute_prefix_embedding(prefix_id)  # ❌ O(n) compute\n        prefix_embeddings[prefix_id] = prefix_emb  # ✅ Cache [web:261]\n    \n    # ✅ Use cached prefix + generate remaining\n    return generate_with_prefix(prompt, prefix_emb)\n\nllm_prefix_tuning(\"Common prompt...\", \"common_prefix\")  # ❌ First: O(n)\nllm_prefix_tuning(\"Common prompt...\", \"common_prefix\")  # ✅ Cached: O(1) [web:261]\n# Time: O(1) cached vs O(n) compute, Space: O(prefix_embeddings) [web:261]"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "When to Use (Decision Criteria)"}]}, {"type": "table", "content": [{"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Scenario"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Time-Space Tradeoff (More Space)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableHeader", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Use Space-Time Tradeoff (Less Space)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Repeated queries"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ LLM caching, prefix caching"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ Recompute every time"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memory-limited"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ Too much memory"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ Compression, quantization"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Performance-critical"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ O(1) cache vs O(n) compute"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ Slow recomputation"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Large datasets"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ Indexing, precomputed tables"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ O(n) scan"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Single query"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "❌ Overhead of cache"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ Recompute (no cache needed)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "tableRow", "content": [{"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Model size"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ FP32 (fast, big)"}]}]}, {"type": "tableCell", "attrs": {"colspan": 1, "rowspan": 1, "colwidth": null, "align": null}, "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "✅ INT8 (slow, small)"}]}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Rule of thumb:"}, {"type": "text", "text": "\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "More space (faster)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Repeated queries, performance-critical, large datasets\n- "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Less space (slower)"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Memory-limited, single query, model size constraints"}]}, {"type": "horizontalRule"}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3}, "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Key Takeaways"}]}, {"type": "orderedList", "attrs": {"start": 1, "type": null}, "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Time-Space Trade-off"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": More space → less time (precompute/cache)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Space-Time Trade-off"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Less space → more time (recompute)"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Memoization"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": O(1) cached vs O(n) recompute"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Lookup Tables"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": O(1) precompute vs O(n) recalc"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Gen AI uses"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Transformer attention caching, LLM response caching, prefix caching, model quantization"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "Tradeoff"}, {"type": "text", "text": ": Choose based on constraints (memory vs. speed)"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Since you're a full-stack engineer working on Gen AI, time/space tradeoffs are essential for optimizing "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "transformer inference"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (caching attention weights for O(1) reuse), implementing "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "LLM response caching"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (O(1) cache vs O(n) generation for repeated queries), and applying "}, {"type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}], "text": "model quantization"}, {"type": "text", "text": " (smaller INT8 models vs. faster FP32 models). Master caching strategies for repeated queries and compression for memory-limited environments."}]}]}}